{"title":"程砚秋同志逝世周年纪念演出观后","authors":["邓拓"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":3,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"程砚秋同志逝世周年纪念演出观后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓拓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"程门立雪岂空谈？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃李而今盛斗南。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独创新腔如怨诉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫将绝艺比青蓝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧时痛洒荒山泪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劲节长留碧玉簪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化鹤千秋遗爱在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无边春草已毵毵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年三月十二日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}